<br>
Our Light is the light of reason, we believe that there is enough evil existing on Norrath that we do not need to create any more by warring with other guilds. Each member is family and has an equal voice. To ease decision making we have an elected leader and Council of representatives who serve the guild.<br>
<br>
In addition, we are a member of The Fellowship, an alliance of similar guilds of neutral to good alignments. The Fellowship regularly holds events for the people of its member guilds; events are a great way to meet alot of nice people.<br>
<br>
